\c 7
\nb
\v 1 IN\nd kosi\nd* yasisithi kuMozisi: Bona, ngikwenze waba njengoNkulunkulu kuFaro\x + 4.16.\x*; loAroni umnewenu uzakuba ngumprofethi wakho\x + Gen. 20.7. 1 Sam. 9.9.\x*.
\v 2 Wena uzakhuluma konke engikulaya khona\x + 4.15; 6.29.\x*; loAroni umnewenu uzakhuluma kuFaro ukuthi ayekele abantwana bakoIsrayeli baphume elizweni lakhe.
\v 3 Kodwa mina ngizakwenza inhliziyo kaFaro ibe lukhuni\x + 4.21.\x*, ngandise\x + 11.9.\x* izibonakaliso\x + 10.1.\x* zami lezimangaliso\x + 11.9.\x* zami elizweni leGibhithe.
\v 4 Kodwa uFaro kayikulilalela; njalo ngizabeka isandla sami phezu kweGibhithe, ngikhuphe amabutho ami, isizwe sami, abantwana bakoIsrayeli, elizweni leGibhithe, ngezigwebo ezinkulu\x + 6.6,26.\x*.
\v 5 Njalo amaGibhithe azakwazi ukuthi ngiyiN\nd kosi\x + 7.17; 8.10,22; 14.4,18.\x*\nd*, lapho ngiselula isandla sami phezu kweGibhithe, ngikhuphe abantwana bakoIsrayeli phakathi kwawo.
\v 6 OMozisi loAroni basebesenza njengoba iN\nd kosi\nd* yabalaya; benza njalo.
\v 7 UMozisi wayeseleminyaka engamatshumi ayisificaminwembili\x + Dute. 29.5; 31.2; 34.7. Seb. 7.23,30.\x*, loAroni wayeleminyaka engamatshumi ayisificaminwembili lantathu lapho bekhuluma kuFaro.
\s Isimangaliso esenziwa ngentonga kaAroni
\p
\v 8 IN\nd kosi\nd* yasikhuluma kuMozisi lakuAroni, isithi:
\v 9 Nxa uFaro ekhuluma lani esithi: Zenzeleni isimangaliso\x + Isa. 7.11. Joha. 2.18; 6.30.\x*; uzakuthi kuAroni: Thatha intonga yakho, u\add yi\add*phosele phansi phambi kukaFaro, izaba yinyoka\x + 4.3; 7.7.10,12,15. Gen. 1.21. Isa. 51.9.\x*.
\p
\v 10 UMozisi loAroni basebengena kuFaro, benza njalo njengoba iN\nd kosi\nd* ilayile; uAroni wasephosela phansi intonga yakhe phambi kukaFaro laphambi kwenceku zakhe, yasisiba yinyoka.
\v 11 UFaro wasebiza laye izazi\x + Gen. 41.8.\x* labathakathi\x + 7.22; 8.7,18,19; 8.7,18; 9.11. Dute. 18.10. 2 Thes. 2.9. 2 Tim. 3.8.\x*; labalumbi beGibhithe\x + Gen. 41.8.\x* labo benza njalo ngamalumbo abo.
\v 12 Ngoba ngulowo lalowo waphosela phansi intonga yakhe, zaba zinyoka; kodwa intonga kaAroni yaginya intonga zabo.
\v 13 Kodwa inhliziyo kaFaro yaba lukhuni\x + 7.22; 8.19; 9.35; 4.21; 9.12; 10.20,27; 11.10; 14.4,8,17.\x*, okokuthi kabalalelanga, njengokutsho kweN\nd kosi\nd*.
\s Inhlupheko yokuqala: Amanzi aphenduka abe ligazi
\p
\v 14 IN\nd kosi\nd* yasisithi kuMozisi: Inhliziyo kaFaro inzima, uyala ukuyekela isizwe sihambe.
\v 15 Yana kuFaro ekuseni; khangela, uzaphuma esiya emanzini, ume uqondane laye ekhunjini lomfula, lentonga eyaphenduka yaba yinyoka ithathe esandleni sakho\x + 4.2,3,17; 17.5.\x*.
\v 16 Uzakuthi kuye: IN\nd kosi\nd* uNkulunkulu wamaHebheru ingithume kuwe isithi\x + 3.18; 5.3; 9.1,13.\x*: Yekela isizwe sami sihambe, singikhonze enkangala\x + 3.12,18.\x*; kodwa khangela, kawulalelanga kuze kube khathesi.
\v 17 Itsho njalo iN\nd kosi\nd*: Ngalokhu uzakwazi ukuthi ngiyiN\nd kosi\x + 5.2,4; 7.5.\x*\nd*; khangela, ngizatshaya ngentonga esesandleni sami phezu kwamanzi asemfuleni, njalo azaphenduka abe ligazi\x + 4.9. Isam. 16.4,6.\x*.
\v 18 Lenhlanzi ezisemfuleni zizakufa, lomfula ube levumba; lamaGibhithe azadinwa yikunatha amanzi emfuleni\x + 7.21,24.\x*.
\p
\v 19 IN\nd kosi\nd* yasisithi kuMozisi: Tshono kuAroni \add uthi\add*: Thatha intonga yakho, welule isandla sakho\x + 8.5,6,16,17; 9.22; 10.12,21; 14.16,21,26.\x* phezu kwamanzi eGibhithe, phezu kwemifula yabo, phezu kwezifula zabo, laphezu kweziziba zabo, laphezu kwamachibi wonke amanzi abo, ukuze abe ligazi. Kuzakuba legazi elizweni lonke leGibhithe, le\add zitsh\add*eni \add ze\add*zihlahla le\add za\add*matshe.
\v 20 UMozisi loAroni basebesenza njalo, njengokulaya kweN\nd kosi\nd*; wasephakamisa intonga, watshaya amanzi ayesemfuleni\x + 17.5.\x* phambi kwamehlo kaFaro laphambi kwamehlo ezinceku zakhe; lawo wonke amanzi ayesemfuleni aphendulwa aba ligazi\x + Hlab. 78.44; 105.29.\x*.
\v 21 Lenhlanzi ezisemfuleni zafa; lomfula waba levumba, kwaze kwathi amaGibhithe ehluleka ukuwanatha amanzi emfuleni\x + 7.18,23.\x*; njalo kwakulegazi elizweni lonke leGibhithe.
\v 22 Labalumbi beGibhithe benza njalo ngamalumbo abo\x + 7.11.\x*, kwaze kwathi inhliziyo kaFaro yaba lukhuni\x + 7.13.\x*, njalo kabalalelanga, njengokutsho kweN\nd kosi\x + 7.3,4.\x*\nd*.
\v 23 UFaro wasetshibilika waya endlini yakhe njalo kayibekanga inhliziyo yakhe lakulokhu.
\v 24 LamaGibhithe wonke agebha amanzi okunatha inhlangothi zonke zomfula, ngoba babengelakunatha emanzini omfula.
\v 25 Lensuku eziyisikhombisa zagcwaliseka emva kokuthi iN\nd kosi\nd* isitshaye umfula.
